{"tid":2035223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"527 各區開花好過死守立法會？？？","createTime":"2020-05-25T18:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T12:43:26.000Z","uid":13513,"like":60,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"068007ce82f8a9e39a646e58f1f2962392e0055d","tid":2035223,"uid":13513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:18:21.000Z","msg":"係：正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係：負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：非5毛/林奠PR/狗 唔信可以隨便起我底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純粹見大家對527出唔出仲有好大分歧 所以想諗個plan C出黎<br />\n<br />\n如果大三罷成功+各區開花 其實可以做到兩邊都想要既野<br />\n<br />\n1.  可以清晰表達到俾國際知 條國歌法我地唔撚想要<br />\n<br />\n2. 各區開花 shopping 有畫面<br />\n<br />\n3. 避免左無謂既送頭（重防 依家好似去到3重水馬）<br />\n<br />\n4. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最重要！</span></span></strong><br />\n如果做到大3罷 （大家小心駕駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）基本上確定左各區都會有一定人數可以參與 減少話如果去夏慤道會怕無人出 增加被咬風險<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21b8c4076ea0b3af87d542ad297b5d273f6c9c3","tid":2035223,"uid":299241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:19:51.000Z","msg":"支持 推"},{"pid":"a12bdff20fd67b781c8309ac38626d260c8bf665","tid":2035223,"uid":13513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:19:59.000Z","msg":"大家有其他諗法就講啦 唔使怕羞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5777d09f3be8d2f74a0ff20dd87128823a27db9e","tid":2035223,"uid":13513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:21:28.000Z","msg":"再兩邊嘈都唔係辦法 一齊好似之前咁發揮小宇宙 諗過好方法出嚟解決件事咪仲好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a3c0ec67c053b34d77da3978f6d81bc8339fff","tid":2035223,"uid":182007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020